<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AI Job Agent — Tailored Resumes in Minutes</title>
<style>
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
  body{font-family:'Segoe UI',system-ui,sans-serif;color:#1e293b;overflow-x:hidden;}
  :root{--blue:#4F46E5;--purple:#7C3AED;--green:#059669;--grad:linear-gradient(135deg,#4F46E5,#7C3AED);}

  /* NAV */
  nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;padding:0 2rem;height:64px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
  .nav-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-weight:800;font-size:16px;color:var(--blue);}
  .nav-logo span{font-size:20px;}
  .nav-links{display:flex;gap:2rem;list-style:none;}
  .nav-links a{text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;color:#64748b;font-weight:500;transition:color 0.2s;}
  .nav-links a:hover{color:var(--blue);}
  .nav-cta{background:var(--grad);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 20px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;}

  /* HERO */
  .hero{min-height:100vh;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f0c29,#302b63,#24243e);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:6rem 2rem 4rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
  .hero::before{content:"";position:absolute;top:-50%;left:-50%;width:200%;height:200%;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 40%,rgba(79,70,229,0.3),transparent 50%),radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 60%,rgba(124,58,237,0.3),transparent 50%);animation:pulse 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;}
  @keyframes pulse{0%{transform:scale(1);}100%{transform:scale(1.1);}}
  .hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:50px;padding:6px 16px;font-size:13px;color:#a5b4fc;margin-bottom:1.5rem;backdrop-filter:blur(8px);}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(2.2rem,6vw,4rem);font-weight:800;color:#fff;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:1.25rem;letter-spacing:-0.5px;}
  .hero h1 span{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#a78bfa,#60a5fa);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;}
  .hero p{font-size:clamp(1rem,2.5vw,1.2rem);color:#94a3b8;max-width:580px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem;line-height:1.75;}
  .hero-btns{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--grad);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:12px;padding:15px 32px;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(79,70,229,0.4);transition:transform 0.2s,box-shadow 0.2s;}
  .btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(79,70,229,0.5);}
  .btn-secondary{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);color:#fff;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);border-radius:12px;padding:15px 32px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;backdrop-filter:blur(8px);transition:all 0.2s;}
  .btn-secondary:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);}
  .hero-scroll{position:absolute;bottom:2rem;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:6px;color:#64748b;font-size:12px;animation:bounce 2s infinite;}
  @keyframes bounce{0%,100%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0);}50%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(6px);}}
  .scroll-dot{width:4px;height:4px;background:#64748b;border-radius:50%;}

  /* SECTIONS COMMON */
  section{padding:5rem 2rem;}
  .container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;}
  .section-tag{display:inline-block;background:rgba(79,70,229,0.08);color:var(--blue);border-radius:20px;padding:4px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.5px;margin-bottom:1rem;}
  .section-title{font-size:clamp(1.6rem,4vw,2.4rem);font-weight:800;margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.2;}
  .section-sub{font-size:15px;color:#64748b;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 3rem;line-height:1.75;}

  /* START NOW */
  .start-section{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0f4ff,#f5f3ff,#ecfdf5);}
  .start-card{background:#fff;border-radius:20px;padding:3rem;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);border:1px solid #e2e8f0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:3rem;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .start-text{flex:1;min-width:280px;}
  .start-text h2{font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:1rem;}
  .start-text p{color:#64748b;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:15px;}
  .start-visual{flex:1;min-width:280px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#EEF2FF,#F5F3FF);border-radius:16px;padding:1.5rem;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;}
  .step-mini{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;}
  .step-mini:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .step-num{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--grad);color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;}
  .step-mini-text{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#334155;}
  .step-mini-sub{font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;}

  /* PROCESS */
  .process-section{background:#fff;}
  .process-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:2rem;margin-top:1rem;}
  .process-card{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fafc,#f0f4ff);border-radius:16px;padding:1.75rem;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;transition:transform 0.2s,box-shadow 0.2s;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
  .process-card::before{content:"";position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:var(--grad);}
  .process-card:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(79,70,229,0.12);}
  .process-icon{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--grad);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:22px;margin-bottom:1rem;}
  .process-card h3{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .process-card p{font-size:13px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.7;}
  .benefit-list{margin-top:10px;padding-left:0;list-style:none;}
  .benefit-list li{font-size:12px;color:#64748b;padding:3px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
  .benefit-list li::before{content:"✓";color:var(--green);font-weight:700;}

  /* NUMBERS */
  .numbers-section{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f0c29,#302b63);}
  .numbers-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:2rem;}
  .number-card{text-align:center;padding:2rem 1rem;}
  .number-val{font-size:3rem;font-weight:800;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#a78bfa,#60a5fa);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;line-height:1;}
  .number-label{font-size:14px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:8px;font-weight:500;}
  .number-sub{font-size:12px;color:#64748b;margin-top:4px;}

  /* REVIEWS */
  .reviews-section{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0f4ff,#f5f3ff);}
  .reviews-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:1.5rem;}
  .review-card{background:#fff;border-radius:16px;padding:1.5rem;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);}
  .review-stars{color:#f59e0b;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:12px;}
  .review-text{font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.25rem;font-style:italic;}
  .reviewer{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
  .reviewer-avatar{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
  .reviewer-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;}
  .reviewer-role{font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;}
  .review-tag{display:inline-block;background:#f0fdf4;color:#059669;border-radius:10px;padding:2px 8px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;margin-top:8px;}

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-section{background:#fff;}
  .faq-list{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;}
  .faq-item{border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:12px;overflow:hidden;}
  .faq-q{padding:1rem 1.25rem;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;background:#f8fafc;transition:background 0.2s;}
  .faq-q:hover{background:#f0f4ff;}
  .faq-icon{font-size:18px;color:var(--blue);transition:transform 0.3s;flex-shrink:0;}
  .faq-a{padding:0 1.25rem;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height 0.3s ease,padding 0.3s ease;font-size:14px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.75;}
  .faq-item.open .faq-a{max-height:200px;padding:1rem 1.25rem;}
  .faq-item.open .faq-icon{transform:rotate(45deg);}

  /* CONTACT */
  .contact-section{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f0c29,#302b63);}
  .contact-inner{display:flex;gap:3rem;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:flex-start;}
  .contact-info{flex:1;min-width:260px;}
  .contact-info h2{font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#fff;margin-bottom:1rem;}
  .contact-info p{color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:15px;}
  .contact-detail{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;color:#a5b4fc;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;}
  .contact-form{flex:1;min-width:280px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:16px;padding:1.75rem;backdrop-filter:blur(8px);}
  .form-group{margin-bottom:1rem;}
  .form-group label{display:block;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .form-group input,.form-group textarea,.form-group select{width:100%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border-radius:8px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:14px;color:#fff;outline:none;font-family:inherit;transition:border-color 0.2s;}
  .form-group input::placeholder,.form-group textarea::placeholder{color:#64748b;}
  .form-group input:focus,.form-group textarea:focus{border-color:#7C3AED;}
  .form-group textarea{resize:vertical;min-height:100px;}
  .form-submit{width:100%;background:var(--grad);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:13px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(79,70,229,0.3);transition:transform 0.2s;}
  .form-submit:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);}

  /* FOOTER */
  footer{background:#0a0a0f;padding:1.5rem 2rem;text-align:center;color:#475569;font-size:13px;border-top:1px solid #1e293b;}

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  .fade-in{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease,transform 0.6s ease;}
  .fade-in.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}

  @media(max-width:600px){
    nav .nav-links{display:none;}
    .start-card{flex-direction:column;}
    .contact-inner{flex-direction:column;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo"><span>🤖</span> AI Job Agent</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#how-it-works">How it works</a></li>
    <li><a href="#reviews">Reviews</a></li>
    <li><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="nav-cta" onclick="window.location.href='https://job-agent-frontend-delta.vercel.app/'">Get Started Free</button>
</nav>

<!-- SECTION 1: HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:750px;">
    <div class="hero-badge">✨ AI-Powered Resume Tailoring</div>
    <h1>Your Resume, <span>Tailored for Every Job</span> in Minutes</h1>
    <p>Stop sending the same resume everywhere. Our AI reads the job description, rewrites your resume to match, and writes your cover letter — all in under 5 minutes.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <button class="btn-primary" onclick="window.location.href='https://job-agent-frontend-delta.vercel.app/'">🚀 Build My Resume Now — Free</button>
      <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="document.getElementById('how-it-works').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">See How It Works</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <div class="scroll-dot"></div>
    <div class="scroll-dot"></div>
    <div class="scroll-dot"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 2: START NOW -->
<section class="start-section" id="start">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="start-card fade-in">
      <div class="start-text">
        <div class="section-tag">GET STARTED</div>
        <h2>Ready to land more interviews?</h2>
        <p>Paste your resume, drop in a job description, and get a fully tailored ATS-optimised resume with a cover letter in minutes. No templates. No guesswork. Pure AI.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <button class="btn-primary" onclick="window.location.href='https://job-agent-frontend-delta.vercel.app/'">🚀 Start Building Now</button>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b;"><span>✓</span> Free to use</div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;margin-top:1.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:12px;color:#059669;font-weight:600;">✓ No credit card</div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:12px;color:#059669;font-weight:600;">✓ Works for all roles</div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:12px;color:#059669;font-weight:600;">✓ ATS optimised</div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:12px;color:#059669;font-weight:600;">✓ Cover letter included</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="start-visual">
        <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#4F46E5;margin-bottom:12px;letter-spacing:0.5px;">YOUR 7-STEP JOURNEY</div>
        <div class="step-mini"><div class="step-num">1</div><div><div class="step-mini-text">Upload or paste your resume</div><div class="step-mini-sub">PDF, DOCX, paste text or fill manually</div></div></div>
        <div class="step-mini"><div class="step-num">2</div><div><div class="step-mini-text">Verify & edit your profile</div><div class="step-mini-sub">AI extracts all details — edit anything</div></div></div>
        <div class="step-mini"><div class="step-num">3</div><div><div class="step-mini-text">Set job preferences</div><div class="step-mini-sub">Role, location, salary, paste any JD</div></div></div>
        <div class="step-mini"><div class="step-num">4</div><div><div class="step-mini-text">AI scores job matches</div><div class="step-mini-sub">See % match + gaps for each job</div></div></div>
        <div class="step-mini"><div class="step-num">5</div><div><div class="step-mini-text">Answer targeted questions</div><div class="step-mini-sub">AI asks what it needs to personalise</div></div></div>
        <div class="step-mini"><div class="step-num">6</div><div><div class="step-mini-text">Get tailored resume + cover letter</div><div class="step-mini-sub">ATS-optimised, keyword-matched</div></div></div>
        <div class="step-mini"><div class="step-num">7</div><div><div class="step-mini-text">Download & apply</div><div class="step-mini-sub">Print to PDF, copy cover letter, apply</div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 3: HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="process-section" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="section-tag">HOW IT WORKS</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Everything you need to land the interview</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Our AI does the heavy lifting — from parsing your resume to tailoring every bullet point for the job you want.</p>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="process-card fade-in">
        <div class="process-icon">🧠</div>
        <h3>AI Resume Parsing</h3>
        <p>Paste or upload your resume in any format. Our AI extracts every detail — contact, skills, experience, education — accurately in seconds.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>Supports PDF, DOCX, plain text</li>
          <li>Extracts all work history</li>
          <li>Fully editable after parsing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="process-card fade-in">
        <div class="process-icon">🎯</div>
        <h3>Smart Job Matching</h3>
        <p>Paste any job description and our AI scores your profile against it, identifies skill gaps, and tells you exactly why you're a fit or not.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>Match score 0-100%</li>
          <li>Gap analysis per job</li>
          <li>Works with any job board</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="process-card fade-in">
        <div class="process-icon">✏️</div>
        <h3>Personalised Questions</h3>
        <p>AI asks you targeted questions based on your resume and the job — to capture achievements and context that make your application stronger.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>Questions unique to each JD</li>
          <li>Captures quantifiable impact</li>
          <li>All optional — skip any</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="process-card fade-in">
        <div class="process-icon">📄</div>
        <h3>ATS-Optimised Resume</h3>
        <p>Your resume is rewritten with the exact keywords from the job description, achievement-focused bullets, and a professional summary that matches the role.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>Keyword matching highlighted</li>
          <li>ATS score estimate shown</li>
          <li>Download as PDF instantly</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="process-card fade-in">
        <div class="process-icon">✉️</div>
        <h3>Cover Letter Included</h3>
        <p>Every tailored resume comes with a 3-paragraph professional cover letter written specifically for the company and role — ready to copy and send.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>Company-specific content</li>
          <li>Professional tone</li>
          <li>One-click copy</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="process-card fade-in">
        <div class="process-icon">🔄</div>
        <h3>Apply to Multiple Jobs</h3>
        <p>Select multiple jobs in one session. Each gets its own tailored resume and cover letter. No repeating steps — results are cached so you never redo work.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>Multiple jobs per session</li>
          <li>Cached — no repeat API calls</li>
          <li>Back/forward freely</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 4: NUMBERS -->
<section class="numbers-section">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="section-tag" style="background:rgba(167,139,250,0.15);color:#a78bfa;">BY THE NUMBERS</div>
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color:#fff;margin-bottom:3rem;">Trusted by job seekers across India</h2>
    <div class="numbers-grid fade-in">
      <div class="number-card">
        <div class="number-val">50K+</div>
        <div class="number-label">Resumes Tailored</div>
        <div class="number-sub">And growing every day</div>
      </div>
      <div class="number-card">
        <div class="number-val">3×</div>
        <div class="number-label">More Interview Callbacks</div>
        <div class="number-sub">Compared to generic resumes</div>
      </div>
      <div class="number-card">
        <div class="number-val">5 min</div>
        <div class="number-label">Average Time to Apply</div>
        <div class="number-sub">From resume to tailored output</div>
      </div>
      <div class="number-card">
        <div class="number-val">20K+</div>
        <div class="number-label">Active Users</div>
        <div class="number-sub">Across all experience levels</div>
      </div>
      <div class="number-card">
        <div class="number-val">92%</div>
        <div class="number-label">ATS Pass Rate</div>
        <div class="number-sub">Average score on tailored resumes</div>
      </div>
      <div class="number-card">
        <div class="number-val">₹0</div>
        <div class="number-label">Cost to Get Started</div>
        <div class="number-sub">Free for your first application</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 5: REVIEWS -->
<section class="reviews-section" id="reviews">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="section-tag">REVIEWS</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">What job seekers are saying</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Real feedback from people who used AI Job Agent to land interviews at top companies.</p>
    <div class="reviews-grid">
      <div class="review-card fade-in">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"I was applying to 10 jobs a week with the same resume and getting no responses. After using this tool, I got 3 interview calls within a week. The keyword matching is insane."</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4F46E5,#7C3AED);">P</div>
          <div><div class="reviewer-name">Priya Sharma</div><div class="reviewer-role">Product Manager · Bangalore</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="review-tag">Got interview at Swiggy</div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card fade-in">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"The AI questions it asks are genuinely smart. It noticed I hadn't mentioned my team size and asked me — that detail ended up being highlighted in the resume and I think that's what got me shortlisted."</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#059669,#0891b2);">A</div>
          <div><div class="reviewer-name">Arjun Mehta</div><div class="reviewer-role">Data Analyst · Mumbai</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="review-tag">Got interview at PhonePe</div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card fade-in">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"I'm a 2024 fresher and had no idea how to tailor my resume. This tool explained the gaps, asked me the right questions, and built a resume that actually sounded professional."</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#D97706,#DC2626);">S</div>
