<!-- SECTION 6: FAQ -->
<section class="faq-section" id="faq">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="section-tag">FAQ</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Everything you need to know before getting started.</p>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is this free to use? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes — you can get started completely free. Parse your resume, view job matches, and preview your tailored resume at no cost. The AI tailoring and cover letter generation are included.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is ATS and why does it matter? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">ATS stands for Applicant Tracking System — software most companies use to filter resumes before a human sees them. If your resume doesn't have the right keywords, it gets rejected automatically. Our AI ensures your resume passes ATS by matching the exact language from the job description.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How is this different from editing my resume myself? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">Manually tailoring takes 30-60 minutes per application and you often miss keywords. Our AI reads the full JD, identifies every relevant keyword, rewrites your bullets to match, and scores the result — all in under 5 minutes. It also asks you targeted questions to surface achievements you might not think to include.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is my resume data safe? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">Your resume is processed securely and never stored permanently. Each session is independent — once you close the browser, your data is not retained. We do not share your data with any third parties.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I use this for multiple job applications? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">Absolutely. You can add multiple job descriptions in a single session and get a separate tailored resume and cover letter for each one. Results are cached so you never have to redo a step — navigate back and forward freely.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What file formats are supported? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">You can upload PDF, DOCX, or TXT files. You can also paste your resume text directly or fill in your details manually using our step-by-step form.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Does it work for all industries and experience levels? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes — the AI adapts to any role, industry, or experience level. Whether you are a fresher, a mid-career professional, or a senior leader making a career switch, the tool tailors your resume to the specific job you are targeting.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How long does it take to get a tailored resume? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">The full process — from uploading your resume to downloading your tailored output — takes under 5 minutes. The AI resume tailoring step itself takes 10-20 seconds on our servers.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

